{"tid":824832,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"王祖藍執導\"純香港電影\", 賀歲檔上映","createTime":"2018-09-17T08:53:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-18T06:43:31.000Z","uid":134071,"like":17,"dislike":379,"uniUserReply":71,"replies":[{"pid":"68fbc1efc19b659d4ed5b0ae73d37101ec9d3f86","tid":824832,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T08:53:22.000Z","msg":"竟然唔係合拍片<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180907/58657678\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180907%2F58657678&d=zY%2FQSSMQZOo%2Fp9VqewScKjOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=e1c86fa2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180907%2F58657678&h=6819d2cd\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180907/58657678</a><br />\n<br />\n王祖藍同李亞男結婚三年，上兩個月公佢哋係網上宣佈終於造人成功(相關新聞： <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2oLbydj\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2oLbydj&d=zY%2FQSSMQZOo%2Fp9VqewScKjOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=1efe7440\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2oLbydj</a> )，預產期應該去明年農曆生年前後。唔知係咁啱，定係神嘅安排，祖藍第一套導演嘅電影《你咪理，我愛你，死未？》（暫名），已經安排喺出年賀歲檔上映，到時真係雙喜臨門。<br />\n<br />\n講番祖藍套處男導演作《你咪理》，係改編自同名嘅舞台劇，故事圍繞男歡女愛，由拍拖到分手、之後結婚生仔、死別嘅段落結合而成。而今次改編成電影，仍然保留歌舞嘅原素，歌舞片賀歲都咪話唔特別。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>今次祖藍嘅電影係純港片元素，所有主要演員都係本地演員。</strong>因為要唱歌跳舞，祖藍就搵咗唱家班嘅杜麗莎同老友阮兆祥演出，主要演員仲有今年憑《黃金花》兩度封影后嘅先姐毛舜筠，佢今次會向演技挑戰，分飾4、5個不同角色。愛情部份就會由人妻岑麗香同方力申擔當，祖藍會自導自演，<br />\n<br />\n<strong>據知，處男下海當導演嘅祖藍不容有失，試過有一個兩分鐘鏡頭，佢足足拍咗14個鐘至收貨。</strong>"},{"pid":"269fef98c00f7f8ece7acf72edd90f88c0882aa0","tid":824832,"uid":81698,"like":6,"dislike":54,"score":-48,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T08:55:00.000Z","msg":"賀歲片？港產片？不了 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adff5cbe969b3754c8247c887a92aee6d3e7b51c","tid":824832,"uid":24368,"like":199,"dislike":7,"score":192,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T08:55:07.000Z","msg":"新年流流死死聲"},{"pid":"ebd030111535fb180bf42cb8071bae97f5a1181d","tid":824832,"uid":134071,"like":49,"dislike":1,"score":48,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T08:57:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>賀歲片？<strong>港產片</strong>？不了 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n見到一D本土派支持者,  都係歧視港產片 (但又日日追大陸劇 ) <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56f5b25f9abd0193812341928d13b1a3e2c3f895","tid":824832,"uid":134071,"like":5,"dislike":38,"score":-33,"quote":{"pid":"adff5cbe969b3754c8247c887a92aee6d3e7b51c","tid":824832,"uid":24368,"like":199,"dislike":7,"score":192,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T08:55:07.000Z","msg":"新年流流死死聲"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T08:58:03.000Z","msg":"黑豹都係死死聲, 但做左賀歲票房No. 1"},{"pid":"de265339d31b2fa3ac664000ca24e089f96fdc8f","tid":824832,"uid":69213,"like":2,"dislike":15,"score":-13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T08:58:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"844128ab9ec20c5551014df8ce8a4b399e456adf","tid":824832,"uid":82912,"like":28,"dislike":1,"score":27,"quote":{"pid":"68fbc1efc19b659d4ed5b0ae73d37101ec9d3f86","tid":824832,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T08:53:22.000Z","msg":"竟然唔係合拍片<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180907/58657678\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180907%2F58657678&d=zY%2FQSSMQZOo%2Fp9VqewScKjOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=e1c86fa2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A